{"id": "ChIJobNaHIO4woARmjJB77L7Heg", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 6416, "displayName": {"text": "BCD Tofu House", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Casual Korean restaurant chain serving classic fare such as soft tofu soup, bibimbap & bulgogi.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJobNaHIO4woARmjJB77L7Heg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoamJFUnVXREJpWTNodFUzWmpXWEpHYlhGb1JuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Nestled in the heart of Ktown in Los Angeles .\nThis place is busy and I understand why.\nThe employees here work around the clock to produce amazing food and great customer experience\nThe customer service is great, and the food is just as much a match\nI was recommended this place from a coworker, and I am glad that I took the time to visit.\nKeep up the good work\nI will return .\nTry them out\nFive stars\n🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Nestled in the heart of Ktown in Los Angeles .\nThis place is busy and I understand why.\nThe employees here work around the clock to produce amazing food and great customer experience\nThe customer service is great, and the food is just as much a match\nI was recommended this place from a coworker, and I am glad that I took the time to visit.\nKeep up the good work\nI will return .\nTry them out\nFive stars\n🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Leah McCarthy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103738169646770582090/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM5eC2bgD1oPG-922rE7TkgI8XcrsQb7LSYkI_2c_PPbfkvj4I=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-04T05:08:25.231796078Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoamJFUnVXREJpWTNodFUzWmpXWEpHYlhGb1JuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoamJFUnVXREJpWTNodFUzWmpXWEpHYlhGb1JuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8831c5ab3a1:0xe81dfbb2ef41329a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobNaHIO4woARmjJB77L7Heg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wR1VEbHhVR0ZVUm5kd00yWjZkVUozU21VNGJHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Drove all the way from the South Bay because the one in Torrance isn’t open late. Ordered the Kalbi and Original tofu soup. Out of the 3 location I’ve eaten, by far this one is the best. Everything came out scolding hot, pretty much burnt my mouth. My server even served my up my rice, I was surprised. I ate alone so they put me in a location where people were by themselves so I didn’t feel like a loner! This place is gonna me my go to. Thank you again for such great service", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Drove all the way from the South Bay because the one in Torrance isn’t open late. Ordered the Kalbi and Original tofu soup. Out of the 3 location I’ve eaten, by far this one is the best. Everything came out scolding hot, pretty much burnt my mouth. My server even served my up my rice, I was surprised. I ate alone so they put me in a location where people were by themselves so I didn’t feel like a loner! This place is gonna me my go to. Thank you again for such great service", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christopher Cangco", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102283225431610804016/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLFFCXjImwmNgE70mPdG0d8SmfDgHHhIheouJiemS2nsrScQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-03T06:12:05.516292938Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wR1VEbHhVR0ZVUm5kd00yWjZkVUozU21VNGJHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wR1VEbHhVR0ZVUm5kd00yWjZkVUozU21VNGJHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8831c5ab3a1:0xe81dfbb2ef41329a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobNaHIO4woARmjJB77L7Heg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0dlVscHpOVlI2VEZGWVEyRTJNa1ZTV0RoTVVrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "BCD Tofu House in LA delivered a reliably satisfying experience, especially if you’re in the mood for comforting Korean food served quickly and generously. The signature soon tofu came out boiling hot with a rich, well-seasoned broth that paired nicely with the soft curds of tofu and your choice of protein. One of the highlights is the complimentary dishes that arrive alongside the stew — from crispy fried fish to fresh kimchi — adding variety and a homestyle feel to the meal. Portions are hearty, rice is perfectly cooked and served in a stone pot for that delicious crust, and service moves at a brisk pace even during busy hours. It’s not a place known for culinary surprises, but if you’re craving classic sundubu done right in the heart of LA’s Korean comfort-food scene, BCD remains a dependable go-to.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "BCD Tofu House in LA delivered a reliably satisfying experience, especially if you’re in the mood for comforting Korean food served quickly and generously. The signature soon tofu came out boiling hot with a rich, well-seasoned broth that paired nicely with the soft curds of tofu and your choice of protein. One of the highlights is the complimentary dishes that arrive alongside the stew — from crispy fried fish to fresh kimchi — adding variety and a homestyle feel to the meal. Portions are hearty, rice is perfectly cooked and served in a stone pot for that delicious crust, and service moves at a brisk pace even during busy hours. It’s not a place known for culinary surprises, but if you’re craving classic sundubu done right in the heart of LA’s Korean comfort-food scene, BCD remains a dependable go-to.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chef on travel", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105500973875085026289/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSvsqrWOJXzaJmo-bnP3-yAzOYm0tDyOGItURf8MT5a1uPvyI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-29T02:28:31.566856949Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0dlVscHpOVlI2VEZGWVEyRTJNa1ZTV0RoTVVrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0dlVscHpOVlI2VEZGWVEyRTJNa1ZTV0RoTVVrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8831c5ab3a1:0xe81dfbb2ef41329a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobNaHIO4woARmjJB77L7Heg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCYVJWTk5VMnR4WlhaemFFTnVObGRpU210YVVIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Ordering delivery from this restaurant is honestly frustrating. The container they use for the soup is ridiculous.\n10 out of 10 times the oil has already leaked out or spills everywhere when I open the lid.\nEverything ends up covered in oil.\nPlease change the packaging. This makes no sense. You should try using it yourselves.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Ordering delivery from this restaurant is honestly frustrating. The container they use for the soup is ridiculous.\n10 out of 10 times the oil has already leaked out or spills everywhere when I open the lid.\nEverything ends up covered in oil.\nPlease change the packaging. This makes no sense. You should try using it yourselves.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ali Khan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103573451293913678526/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaatBOQJCjDVX3_Zc1jSNRabm_evw6IG-ccU-R_GbbnQGsKw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-06T09:02:51.698922645Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCYVJWTk5VMnR4WlhaemFFTnVObGRpU210YVVIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCYVJWTk5VMnR4WlhaemFFTnVObGRpU210YVVIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8831c5ab3a1:0xe81dfbb2ef41329a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobNaHIO4woARmjJB77L7Heg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kNVIyUmFUVFJxWmpsUmJHaDZiMUJEZW5GQk5uYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This is the OG BCD. You gotta try it if you're ever in LA.\n\n+Service is fast and they're on it.\n+The Korean food is legit and super tasty.\n+The side dishes are good too, and there's a nice variety.\n+It's spicy, but not too salty.\n+I'd totally recommend the Tofu Stew and the LA rib set.\n\n-It gets packed though, so you might have to wait.\n-I get that it's busy, but they were cleaning the table right next to me while I was still eating. They just tossed all the leftovers in the trash. Not exactly a fun experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is the OG BCD. You gotta try it if you're ever in LA.\n\n+Service is fast and they're on it.\n+The Korean food is legit and super tasty.\n+The side dishes are good too, and there's a nice variety.\n+It's spicy, but not too salty.\n+I'd totally recommend the Tofu Stew and the LA rib set.\n\n-It gets packed though, so you might have to wait.\n-I get that it's busy, but they were cleaning the table right next to me while I was still eating. They just tossed all the leftovers in the trash. Not exactly a fun experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Harry HM", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100734485268663931371/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDtZ08wUm9bUQRG_cgyhDJE_j7KVcHH4TQdFf03qGCfa3FWkY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-15T09:52:52.745148407Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kNVIyUmFUVFJxWmpsU